# Docker build context: repo root (for openclaw-image builds).
# Exclude everything, then whitelist only what the Dockerfile needs.
*

# OpenClaw submodule
!magister-openclaw/

# Marketing skills submodule
!magister-marketingskills/skills/

# Custom Magister skills (repo root)
!skills/

# Build assets from openclaw-image/
!openclaw-image/default-config/
!openclaw-image/entrypoint.sh
